; Coverage test for filters.cc
; Tests changed_value_posts::output_intermediate_prices with price changes
; between postings. The --market --revalued options trigger revaluation
; generation. Lines 840-841: AMOUNT type path in output_intermediate_prices.

P 2024/01/01 AAPL 100 $
P 2024/02/01 AAPL 150 $

2024/01/15 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage          10 AAPL
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/15 Buy More
    Assets:Brokerage          5 AAPL
    Assets:Cash

test reg --market --revalued brokerage
24-Jan-15 Buy                   Assets:Brokerage              $1000        $1000
24-Feb-01 Commodities revalued  <Revalued>                     $500        $1500
24-Feb-15 Buy More              Assets:Brokerage               $750        $2250
end test
